flowchart LR
  F0["F0 Source Intake<br/>Collect the raw paper and every source without judging too early."]
  F1["F1 Source Resolution<br/>Separate raw facts, claims, conflicts, decisions, and guesses."]
  F2["F2 Product SOT<br/>Create the product source of truth agents must obey."]
  F3["F3 Understanding Alignment<br/>Ask only questions that change risk, architecture, product, or execution."]
  F4["F4 Architecture Candidate<br/>Design the product from the SOT and constraints."]
  F5["F5 Product Face<br/>Define screens, states, wallet flows, mobile, a11y, performance, and visual evidence."]
  F6["F6 Specialist Reviews<br/>Security, cyber, Solana, frontend, backend, QA, DevOps, CTO review the architecture."]
  F7["F7 Onchain Package<br/>For Solana/Quasar: accounts, ABI, PDA, CPI, compute units, authorities, Auditor."]
  F8["F8 Security Scan Plan<br/>Define scan timing, scope, owner, tools, acceptance, and blocking policy."]
  F9["F9 Human Architecture Gate<br/>Human approves, rejects, or sends architecture back to revision."]
  F10["F10 Documentation OS<br/>Turn architecture into specs, decisions, contracts, diagrams, and evidence paths."]
  F11["F11 Decomposition<br/>Create gated Hermes cards with owner, executor, reviewer, risk, surfaces, and done contract."]
  F12["F12 Execution<br/>Agents execute bounded work without expanding authority."]
  F13["F13 Verification<br/>Run tests, scans, screenshots, Auditor, and domain checks."]
  F14["F14 Independent Review<br/>A different reviewer validates the work and evidence."]
  F15["F15 Human R3/R4 Gate<br/>High-risk work needs explicit human approval and rollback ownership."]
  F16["F16 Promotion<br/>Promote only when evidence, review, security, rollback, and monitoring are ready."]
  F17["F17 Production Monitoring<br/>Watch runtime health, product behavior, and release safety."]
  F18["F18 Learning Loop<br/>Convert pilot lessons into Factory VNext."]

  F0 --> F1 --> F2 --> F3 --> F4 --> F5 --> F6 --> F7 --> F8 --> F9 --> F10 --> F11 --> F12 --> F13 --> F14 --> F15 --> F16 --> F17 --> F18

  H["Hermes Adapter<br/>Kanban gates enforce transitions; agents cannot bypass weak cards or missing receipts."]
  G1["Ready Gate<br/>Blocks missing Product Face, Auditor, security scan packet, R4 gate, or distinct reviewer."]
  G2["Done Gate<br/>Requires Receipt Five, transition event, scan results, and risk-class evidence."]
  G3["Exit Code Enforcement<br/>Blocked transitions return non-zero so scripts cannot treat failure as success."]

  F11 --> H
  H --> G1
  H --> G2
  H --> G3
